Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:11.88,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,背上的羽翼　已经与你一同消失
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.88,0:00:19.68,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,飞翔时的记忆　却无法像擦伤一样消去
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.86,0:00:35.99,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,将你寻回　是我一直所想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.99,0:00:43.66,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,让你不随时间的浊流　被浪冲走
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.66,0:00:51.46,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,无法说出些许回忆　始终无依无靠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.46,0:00:59.47,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,残留下的些许眼泪　却一定无法传达给你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.47,0:01:05.73,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的泪滴　也将坠落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.73,0:01:13.61,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,突然间黑夜被撕裂　光芒飞散于空中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:21.58,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,洁净如洗的太阳　温柔地照耀着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.58,0:01:26.21,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,怀抱着你一起前进
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.93,0:22:39.27,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,After the rain　等到雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.44,0:22:46.53,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,across the rainbow　就飞越彩虹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:53.58,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,在彩虹被蓝天遮掩前　告诉它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:23:02.00,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,唯一的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:10.59,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,不知为何会被忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.05,0:23:16.06,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,宝物的所在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.48,0:23:25.98,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,After the rain　等到雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:33.24,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,across the rainbow　从哪里开始说起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.24,0:23:40.16,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,悲伤不会消失　所以悄悄地
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:49.47,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,把这些点缀在快乐的回忆里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:02:03.34,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,250)}{\fad(1000,0)}黎明时分的小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾琳崭新的生活开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.82,0:01:39.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和养蜂人约翰一起生活的艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:42.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要到一个叫萨莉姆的城市里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.22,0:01:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,采购些山里所需的日用品
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.78,0:01:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看 那里就是萨莉姆了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.97,0:02:10.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好热闹啊 这么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.84,0:02:14.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里可是商业街啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.62,0:02:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全国的商人和物品都会聚集到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.25,0:02:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些人在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.60,0:02:23.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要过去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是街头乐师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿越不同的城市做着表演
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家前来捧场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.00,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明天就要离开这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.27,0:03:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有幸能与大家在别处相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.32,0:03:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.65,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最喜欢妈妈了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你吵醒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能够和妈妈一起睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也好 两个人一起会更暖和些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您…怎么不弹了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:55.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚弹奏的曲子叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:05:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明时分的小鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.61,0:05:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黎明时分的小鸟?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:06.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来柔和悦耳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 艾琳 你在那儿干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.72,0:05:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叔叔 刚才…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.83,0:05:17.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.45,0:05:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没什么啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑 别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.10,0:05:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肚子好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候要是把斗蛇蛋弄到手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.94,0:05:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在早就赚翻天了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好意思说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.57,0:05:56.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是已经发誓 要为了那个死去的小姑娘认真活下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.93,0:05:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要下定决心好好的工作挣钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.46,0:06:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是 莫库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:05.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.89,0:06:07.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.62,0:06:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫库
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.04,0:06:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.84,0:06:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋 跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好 是官员
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.73,0:06:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是为偷蛋的事来抓我们的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.21,0:06:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在要去的这家店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.80,0:06:29.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卖的柿子饼好吃到让人垂涎三尺哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没人在的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平日里都是让她儿子塔尔加看店的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠安家的店没开了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.20,0:06:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.16,0:06:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说突然病倒了而且卧床不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.45,0:06:53.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儿子去服劳役了也不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可怜呐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:06:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了 在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.09,0:07:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 塔尔加吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.87,0:07:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.47,0:07:08.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.18,0:07:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.36,0:07:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.11,0:07:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.99,0:07:32.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:36.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尔加…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.08,0:07:39.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个是我弄来的药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.29,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你老实一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.09,0:07:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我儿子犯了什么罪
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.56,0:07:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在劳役中途伺机逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:54.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个罪可不轻哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.35,0:08:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到妈妈病倒的消息…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.88,0:08:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找了这个药…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请念我儿一片孝心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我替他受罚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 你要不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.43,0:08:14.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.12,0:08:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.09,0:08:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.80,0:08:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了 你给我安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.71,0:08:46.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让他和母亲好好做个分别
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.41,0:08:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.64,0:08:54.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子可是罪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.03,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.31,0:09:15.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给他们几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是…难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.86,0:09:48.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.96,0:09:49.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要紧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:52.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我送你回去 赶紧休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠安太太的病能治好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.04,0:10:24.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,药虽然喝下了但是不敢保证
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要看今晚的情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.14,0:11:07.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼得蛮有调的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,躺在我身旁的小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今夜也要乖乖睡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.14,0:11:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这首歌的歌词嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 我今天第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.32,0:11:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次听到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这首歌叫做"黎明时分的小鸟"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.46,0:11:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢 算是摇篮曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人用竖琴弹的就是这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.31,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拦住官员的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.36,0:11:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个武功高强的人还会弹竖琴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.82,0:11:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动作像"坚盾"般的敏捷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.27,0:11:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚盾?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.87,0:11:52.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚盾是作为真王陛下的护盾的王族护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.50,0:11:55.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过严格训练出来的最强将士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.99,0:11:57.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有这种人?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.64,0:12:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服从严格的规矩 和家人完全脱离关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.35,0:12:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坚强的活着
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规矩…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.66,0:12:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须守规矩 才能活下去…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:47.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.80,0:12:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尔加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.89,0:13:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.69,0:13:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不能做引人注目的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.62,0:13:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白天的那件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.33,0:13:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意气用事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:34.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是无法胜任真王陛下的坚盾之职的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.45,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.09,0:13:38.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有任务
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:42.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是出现在斗蛇众村子的偷蛋贼画像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.11,0:13:44.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一经发现立即逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,问出他们准备把蛋卖给谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.67,0:13:49.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不择手段
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.23,0:14:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来药起效了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.52,0:14:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算让人松了一口气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.15,0:14:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,约翰先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尔加…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.21,0:14:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劳役逃跑者好像会被送往北方的矿山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.82,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.63,0:14:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个傻孩子 为了我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.67,0:14:55.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.43,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫库
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.59,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.02,0:15:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.03,0:15:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:08.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘不得了了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.86,0:15:11.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.62,0:15:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是偷蛋贼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…没偷着的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.68,0:15:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁指使你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 我全部都说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部交代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.55,0:15:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在斗蛇村有人告诉我 说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.92,0:15:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要能拿到蛋就能赚大钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.47,0:15:33.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.12,0:15:54.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:03.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.88,0:16:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:22.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙就是神速的伊亚尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.92,0:16:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的确是动作敏捷如闪电
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:57.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.72,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.91,0:17:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我下次不敢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别杀我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 小姑娘 莫库
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.02,0:17:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个家伙?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:10.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莫库 叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:19.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西叫什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斗蛇村里的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.17,0:17:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芝麻蒸豆腐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫我们俩去偷蛋的那个人叫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.58,0:17:31.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男的 是叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.05,0:17:34.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.63,0:17:40.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.40,0:17:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.32,0:17:45.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:06.89,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}並べ枕の 愛しきわが子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:15.05,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}今宵もう 眠れ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:32.94,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}枕並べの 月の夜には 蛙の声も
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:38.54,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}夜明けの鳥よ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:43.67,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}声が流れて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:51.90,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}しじまを乱す
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:19:01.76,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}なくな 夜明けの鳥よ なくな
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:11.15,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}そなたの声を 思い出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:19.86,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}眠る吐息に 朝霧踊る
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:32.19,song,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}今宵も眠れ 愛しきそなたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:18:06.89,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}躺在我身旁的小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:15.05,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}今夜也要乖乖睡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:32.94,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}月儿轻轻照着你 蛙儿也在柔声唱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.34,0:18:38.54,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}黎明时分的小鸟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:43.67,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}轻轻地鸣叫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.77,0:18:51.90,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}打破了这宁静的夜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:19:01.76,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}不要叫 黎明时分的小鸟啊 不要叫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.97,0:19:11.15,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}会让我想起你声音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.15,0:19:19.86,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}你安静的呼吸 朝雾升起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.86,0:19:32.19,sogtra,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}今夜也要乖乖睡 我亲爱的小宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.40,0:18:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这首歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:36.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很喜欢这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到它就让我想起了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.22,0:18:46.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弹的时候也非常的柔情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你既然能弹出那般温柔的琴声
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.78,0:18:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也请你不要那么残忍伤害我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.83,0:19:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:29.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.56,0:19:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.61,0:19:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 请保重
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.52,0:19:57.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢您的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:19:58.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保证身体
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠安太太
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要静心等待塔尔加回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.41,0:20:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塔尔加会回来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.14,0:20:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 他是个既孝顺又坚强的男孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.43,0:20:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们又一次的被小姑娘救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.77,0:20:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是就是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.78,0:20:28.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不把这恩报了就决不能离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.07,0:20:31.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…那个大叔蛮可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.60,0:20:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说了 决不能离开 决不能离开
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.90,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.83,0:20:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.75,0:20:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.13,0:20:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.97,0:20:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人叫我把这个东西送给有绿色眼瞳的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.24,0:21:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.56,0:21:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.71,0:21:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的天真迟早会害你丢掉性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们可是坚盾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要铭记于心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.90,0:21:33.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊亚尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这竖琴真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.44,0:22:07.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,年轻人送的竖琴上刻有伊亚尔的字样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.27,0:22:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么他会送竖琴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.17,0:22:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾琳还不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.45,0:22:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过他弹奏的那首"黎明时分的小鸟"的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.80,0:22:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对艾琳来说却是难以忘记的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.82,0:24:02.97,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}喂 莫库
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.01,0:24:06.09,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}小姑娘住的那间屋子里面有秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.09,0:24:08.00,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}哇 最喜欢甜甜的蜂蜜了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.00,0:24:10.76,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}不是蜂蜜啦 是秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.76,0:24:14.57,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}小姑娘好像打开了那扇秘密之门
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.67,0:24:16.87,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}那艾琳会变怎样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.87,0:24:19.18,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们现在不是要去看看吗 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.25,0:24:21.05,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}擅自闯进去会挨骂的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.48,0:24:23.03,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}兽之奏者 艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.20,0:24:24.62,toDefault2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an2}门的里面
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.00,0:24:30.00,title2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(352,240)}门的里面
